data.name: button20.ToolTip
data.value: Group A: Custom SCR Battery chargers, UPS, Inverters and SUPPLIER’S modified PRODUCTS, sold at the current multiplier for the specific market it is intended for. Group B: Custom SCR Battery chargers, UPS, Inverters and SUPPLIER’S modified PRODUCTS, sold at a discounted price or through approved reseller. Group C: Standard SCR Battery chargers and SUPPLIER’S modified PRODUCTS sold at the regular multiplier. Group D: Switch Mode Battery chargers and SUPPLIER’S modified PRODUCTS, sold at the regular multiplier. Group E: Batteries, racks, accessories and all SUPPLIER’S non-modified items, sold at the quoted price. Group F: Batteries, racks, accessories and all SUPPLIER’S non-modified items, sold at a discounted price.
